{"title":"Saroj Pathak","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Saroj Pathak","format":{"html":{"css":"styles.css","toc":false,"page-layout":"full","include-in-header":{"text":"<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Data-driven analysis of Nepal's public finance, governance, and political economy — with a focus on subnational fiscal systems and intergovernmental transfers.\">\n"}}}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- ============ NAVBAR ============ -->\n<nav class=\"sp-nav\">\n  <a href=\"/\" class=\"sp-nav-name\">Home</a>\n  <ul class=\"sp-nav-links\">\n    <li><a href=\"/research.html\">Research</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/tools.html\">Tools</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/about.html\">About</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/contact.html\">Contact</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->\n<section class=\"sp-hero\">\n  <span class=\"sp-hero-label\">Public Finance &amp; Policy Analytics · Nepal</span>\n  <h1 class=\"sp-hero-name\">Saroj Pathak</h1>\n  <p class=\"sp-hero-descriptor\">\n    I analyse Nepal's fiscal and governance data to support better \n    public decisions — turning <em>administrative records governments \n    produce but rarely interrogate</em> into evidence that decision-makers \n    can act on.\n  </p>\n  <a href=\"/research.html\" class=\"sp-hero-cta\">\n    View research &nbsp;→\n  </a>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ DIVIDER ============ -->\n<div class=\"sp-rule\"><hr></div>\n\n<!-- ============ RECENT RESEARCH ============ -->\n<section class=\"sp-research\">\n  <div class=\"sp-section-header\">\n    <h2 class=\"sp-section-title\">Recent Research</h2>\n    <a href=\"/research.html\" class=\"sp-view-all\">All briefs →</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sp-cards\">\n```\n\n::: {#recent-research}\n:::\n\n```{=html}\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ DIVIDER ============ -->\n<div class=\"sp-rule\"><hr></div>\n\n<!-- ============ FOCUS AREAS ============ -->\n<section class=\"sp-focus\">\n  <span class=\"sp-section-label\">What I work on</span>\n  <div class=\"sp-focus-grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"sp-focus-item\">\n      <span class=\"sp-focus-item-label\">01</span>\n      <div class=\"sp-focus-item-title\">Public Finance &amp; Fiscal Transfers</div>\n      <p class=\"sp-focus-item-desc\">\n        Analysis of intergovernmental conditional grants, subnational \n        budget allocation, and equity in federal resource distribution \n        across Nepal's 753 local governments.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"sp-focus-item\">\n      <span class=\"sp-focus-item-label\">02</span>\n      <div class=\"sp-focus-item-title\">Governance &amp; Decentralisation</div>\n      <p class=\"sp-focus-item-desc\">\n        How federal policy intent translates — or fails to translate — \n        into subnational outcomes. Focus on Nepal's post-2015 federal \n        transition and its implementation gaps.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"sp-focus-item\">\n      <span class=\"sp-focus-item-label\">03</span>\n      <div class=\"sp-focus-item-title\">Electoral &amp; Political Analytics</div>\n      <p class=\"sp-focus-item-desc\">\n        Constituency-level diagnostic analysis of voter behaviour, \n        party fragmentation, and electoral volatility to support \n        evidence-based campaign strategy.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->\n<footer class=\"sp-footer\">\n  <span class=\"sp-footer-name\">Saroj Pathak · Kathmandu, Nepal</span>\n  <ul class=\"sp-footer-links\">\n    <li><a href=\"mailto:your@email.com\">Email</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"https://github.com/yourusername\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile\" target=\"_blank\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</footer>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- ============ NAVBAR ============ -->\n<nav class=\"sp-nav\">\n  <a href=\"/\" class=\"sp-nav-name\">Home</a>\n  <ul class=\"sp-nav-links\">